flowchart TB
  %% Diagram 19: Payment Gateway Integration Flow

  Start([Buyer Checkout]) --> Select{Select Payment Method}

  Select --> BK[bKash PGW]
  Select --> NG[Nagad PGW]
  Select --> SSL[SSLCommerz]
  Select --> BQR[Bangla QR]
  Select --> RK[Rocket]

  BK --> PI[Create Payment Intent]
  NG --> PI
  SSL --> PI
  BQR --> PI
  RK --> PI

  PI --> Auth[Buyer Authenticates at Provider]
  Auth --> Callback[Gateway Callback or Webhook]

  Callback --> Sig{Signature Valid?}
  Sig -- No --> Reject[Reject Callback\nLog Security Event]
  Reject --> Support[Fraud Monitoring and Support Review]
  Sig -- Yes --> Verify{Provider Transaction Verified?}

  Verify -- No --> Decline[Provider Timeout or Decline]
  Decline --> Failed[Mark Payment Failed\nKeep Order Unconfirmed]
  Failed --> EmitFail[Emit PaymentFailed Event\nReturn Recovery Options]
  Verify -- Yes --> Idem{Duplicate Callback for Same Reference?}
  Idem -- Yes --> NoOp[Return 200 Idempotent No-Op]
  Idem -- No --> Confirm[Mark Payment Confirmed]

  Confirm --> Emit[Emit PaymentConfirmed Event]
  Emit --> Saga[Continue Order Saga\nHold Escrow for Prepaid Orders]
  Saga --> Notify[Notify Buyer and Vendor]

  EmitFail --> RetryChoice{Retry Same Method?}
  RetryChoice -- Yes --> PI
  RetryChoice -- No --> Select

  Emit --> Audit[Append Audit Trail + Correlation ID]
  EmitFail --> Audit
  NoOp --> Audit
